    "To thoroughly assess the effectiveness of the proposed M-DQN model, we examine the results that demonstrate the profitability and risk level of the trading strategies, using ROI and SR as metrics, respectively.",
    "We compared these outcomes with those of similar studies that employ different methodologies for efficient trading strategies, to obtain a better understanding of the performance of the proposed model.",
    "This comparative analysis not only enabled us to pinpoint the areas in which the proposed model excels but also helped identify the aspects that may need further improvement.",
    "Through this evaluation, valuable insights were acquired into the robustness of our approach and its potential for real-world applications in trading strategies.",
    "The results of previous studies are compared with those of the proposed method in Table 8."
